{"tid":757203,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[Siri 的恐怖解謎] 封閉的惡夢 Closed Nightmare","createTime":"2018-07-26T15:30:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T17:15:42.000Z","uid":15867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"28a8fa4027848182f2e48849056eaf7e7b1089e0","tid":757203,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:30:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/232508_b4ab4875e473e3d1f44475ba8ab5253d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F232508_b4ab4875e473e3d1f44475ba8ab5253d.png&h=769b8431&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/232511_c0fd401055fe2054ffe9ef3064a4d538.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F232511_c0fd401055fe2054ffe9ef3064a4d538.png&h=a2be16d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://go.twitch.tv/sirihoihoi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgo.twitch.tv%2Fsirihoihoi&d=OPD9cJfrTgNCAJ8V4Ap8jjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=9b2cdc8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://go.twitch.tv/sirihoihoi</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">台已開～一齊入黎玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n劇場型恐怖冒險遊戲《CLOSED NIGHTMARE 封閉的惡夢》是結合了寫實影像與冒險遊戲的全新恐怖娛樂。最大的特徵是使用寫實影像的呈現方式，事件場景以能夠體驗主角看見的場景的第一人稱視角影片進行。<br />\n<br />\n　　玩家是在一片陰暗且什麼都沒有的房間醒來之喪失記憶的女性。在混亂之中突然響起的電話中傳來小孩的聲音......。「妳是上代真莉亞，本實驗的參加者。」、「妳要負責進行某個任務。」。 在一無所知的情形下，真莉亞只能往前邁進。儘管此時的她完全不知道，接下來將要面對無數不可理喻的恐怖――<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/232937_16d34f210a6d9968c389a47671bc1770.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F232937_16d34f210a6d9968c389a47671bc1770.png&h=7e917307&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/232938_11dfdb01cb16ab31b265977957217f2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F232938_11dfdb01cb16ab31b265977957217f2d.png&h=43008a13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91c1863e79c1646691ffe01294ec594239ca18f3","tid":757203,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ad6b3fe4b2e85a7c331bbd91b65421caee7ef0","tid":757203,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5256d17f11a26ca46cbb1577aa6c700c5fed0490","tid":757203,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deae6e56271e1d3263dbecda4d23b246af1a234d","tid":757203,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:32:32.000Z","msg":"早兩日見到 好似未有二手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚太恐怖無買到"},{"pid":"320f732201336e9edd398ebe668dc1918f82f831","tid":757203,"uid":15867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T17:00:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset